snippet.title: Richard Dawkins & Amber Heard - Atheist Charities Question - VIP Arizona 2019
snippet.description:
Richard Dawkins answers Atheist Charity question with Amber Heard and Robyn Blummer at the VIP event in Mesa, Arizona for his book tour...  Being atheist "probably saved my life."

He says his Non-Believing Foundation raised $500,000 in a few weeks for Haiti after their earthquakes and atheists are giving. Robyn replies about secular countries with social services.

My question was about how religious charities get poor people to become religious and that there should be atheist charities as well as social services...

- When we are atheist it means we are "more likely to DO something" because no one else will.

snippet.title: Top 7 Facts - Amber Heard // Top Facts
snippet.description:
Top 7 Facts - Amber Heard // Top Facts
These and other interesting Top Facts  you can know in this channel.
------------------
1. Amber Laura Heard (born April 22, 1986) is an American actress. Amber Heard was born in Austin, Texas, the daughter of Patricia Paige , an internet researcher, and David Clinton Heard, a contractor.

2. While in Los Angeles, Heard made appearances in several TV shows and two music videos, Kenny Chesney's "There Goes My Life" and Eisley's "| Wasn't Prepared".

3. In late 2008, she filmed The River Why and The Joneses; two independent features. Variety highly praised Heard's acting performance, saying "she steals the show" and that she actually delivered better work than film's leading star Demi Moore in The Joneses.

4. At the beginning of 2009, The lnformers made its premiere at the Sundance Film Festival. Despite an all-star cast, the movie received generally negative reviews. Heard next appeared in Zombieland, playing a small role as the object of Jesse Eisenberg‚Äôs affection who turns into a zombie.

5. In March, Heard began filming The Rum Diary, opposite Johnny Depp,in Puerto Rico. Heard was reported to have won the role out over Scarlett Johansson and Keira Knightley. In 2010, she starred in and produced And Soon the Darkness, co-starring Odette Vustman and Karl Urban.

6. International Business Times described Heard as "talented enough to share a few heartfelt moments in a character that mostly operates on the defensive."

7. On July 16, 2015, Heard was charged by the Australian government for two counts of illegally importing the dogs into the country and one count of producing a false document. If convicted, she could face a prison sentence of up to 11 years and a AU$102,000 ?

snippet.title: Amber Heard's Small Birth Family
snippet.description:
Amber Heard is a young Hollywood actress and a stunning model  whose professional career gains momentum due to extraordinary roles in movies and not only. She dreamt of becoming a famous film performer and in order to make this dream come true, she worked hard to pay for portfolio as well as filming in the studio. At 16, Amber moved to New York to start modeling career. Her bright beauty and beautiful body let her reach success without putting much effort. With the time, modeling sphere began weighing down and Heard moved to LA to ‚Äúconquer‚Äù the Hollywood. She started from playing bit roles in various projects such as The O.C. and Jack and Bobby. However, even these minor roles, helped her to get certain success and she was noticed by many film directors. In such a way, she can be seen in Friday Night Lights, North Country, Never Back Down, Pineapple Express, Magic Mike XXL and so many other works.

Amber‚Äôs father David is an actor in his own right. Knowing how hard an actor‚Äôs life is, he never wanted a daughter to be involved in the filmmaking industry. Nonetheless, it was Amber‚Äôs dream and she followed it. Later, David admitted that she made the right decision and is very proud of her. Both father and daughter can be seen at different events and on a red carpet together.

Meanwhile, a mother Paige is an IT person, who creates websites. In accordance with the actress, her mother is the best parent she could have ever had. Paige has always been supporting the daughter as well as taught her many things in life. 

The stunning movie star has a younger sister named Whitney, who is also an actress. Both sisters are extremely close and are often seen together at different parties and events. Nothing much is known about Whitney‚Äôs personal life, but there is a rumor that she is dating an actor Ryan Adams. 

That is all.
